      <title>捷克央行行长重申谨慎降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/czech-central-bank-chief-reiterates-vow-to-cut-rates-cautiously</link>
      <description><![CDATA[捷克央行行长阿莱斯·米歇尔重申将“非常谨慎”地采取货币宽松政策，以避免引发通胀再度抬头。]]></description>
