      <title>日本生命将在下半年削减日元债券持有量</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/nippon-life-to-cut-yen-bond-holdings-in-fiscal-second-half</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本生命保险公司计划在截至2025年3月的财年下半年减少所持有的日元债券，为更高的利率做准备。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/nippon-life-to-cut-yen-bond-holdings-in-fiscal-second-half</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 08:04:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
